---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="About Compressly – Compress PDF Online"
  description="Compressly is a free, browser-based tool to compress images and PDFs online. No signup, no server upload, fully private."
  canonical="/about"
>
<section class="section">
  <div class="container" style="max-width:720px;">
    <p class="mono-eyebrow" style="margin-bottom:16px;">About Us</p>
    <h1 class="heading-lg" style="margin-bottom:24px;">What is Compressly — Compress PDF Online?</h1>
    <p class="body-lg" style="color:var(--body); margin-bottom:16px;">
      Compressly is a completely free, browser-based file compression tool. 
      It compresses images (JPG, PNG, WEBP) and PDF files directly in your browser — 
      no server upload, no account required.
    </p>
    <p class="body-lg" style="color:var(--body); margin-bottom:32px;">
      We built Compressly because other tools are slow, require signups, 
      have file size limits, or upload your files to servers. We think that's wrong.
    </p>
    <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(200px,1fr)); gap:16px; margin-bottom:48px;">
      <div class="feature-card" style="text-align:center;">
        <div style="font-size:32px; margin-bottom:8px;">🔒</div>
        <p class="heading-md" style="margin-bottom:8px;">100% Private</p>
        <p class="body-md" style="color:var(--body);">Files never leave your device</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card" style="text-align:center;">
        <div style="font-size:32px; margin-bottom:8px;">⚡</div>
        <p class="heading-md" style="margin-bottom:8px;">Instant</p>
        <p class="body-md" style="color:var(--body);">No upload wait time</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card" style="text-align:center;">
        <div style="font-size:32px; margin-bottom:8px;">🆓</div>
        <p class="heading-md" style="margin-bottom:8px;">Free Forever</p>
        <p class="body-md" style="color:var(--body);">No limits, no paywall</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <a href="/" class="btn-primary">Start Compressing →</a>
  </div>
</section>
</Base>
